      "name": "Synthesis of hemolysis modelling evidence from prior centrifugal pump studies",
      "description": "This result consolidates findings from a broad body of published literature on CFD-based hemolysis prediction in rotary blood pumps, including studies by Grigioni et al. (2005), Arvand et al. (2005), Taskin et al. (2012), and Fraser et al. (2012). The synthesis demonstrates consistent model accuracy across device geometries and operating regimes, establishing the general validity of the power-law hemolysis model applied here. The breadth of corroborating evidence from independent research groups substantially increases confidence in the modelling approach adopted for this COU.",
